project_info:
Run as far as you can while facing fateful enemies, crash them, take their biscuits and go to buy some coffee because every hero needs a coffee break to get stronger.
More biscuits, More weapons, heroes and enemies and don't forget MORE COFFEE!
Do not hesitate to shoot or else you die.
Challenge your friends with Google Play leaderboard support and be #1 of your friends. Show off with your weapon, hero and enemy set-up.

FEATURES:
● Simple gameplay - Just click!
● Simple UI Design - Get anywhere you need fast and easy!
● Unique pixel art design for a wonderful play time
● Over 4000 set-up combinations for your own game experience.
● Over 50 different items for you to collect. (And adding even more!)
● Google Play Leaderboard support - Be #1 from your friends and in the WORLD!
● Google Play 'Saved Games' - Get your save on any phone with Play Services Cloud save support!
●Unlock different Achievements while you play the game!

Get in touch with us!
For any bug reports, suggestions or support contact us at RabbitRabbitGames@gmail.com
